Well, my test table as follows

```
CREATE TABLE `TEST_SHARDING_ORDER` (
  `ORDER_ID` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `CUSTOMER` varchar(63) DEFAULT NULL,
  `SUPPLIER` varchar(63) DEFAULT NULL,
  `NOTE` varchar(63) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ORDER_DATE` datetime(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `LAST_UPDATED_STAMP` datetime(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`ORDER_ID`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8
```
```

import java.io.IOException;
import java.sql.Connection;
import java.sql.DriverManager;
import java.sql.PreparedStatement;
import java.sql.Timestamp;

public class Sharding {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        String idKeyValue = "100006";
        int sharding = Math.abs(String.valueOf(idKeyValue).hashCode() % 17);

        System.out.println("sharding is " + sharding);

        String jdbcUrl = "jdbc:mysql://192.168.101.24:3307/sharding_db?autoReconnect=true&useUnicode=true&characterEncoding=UTF-8&useSSL=false";
        String username = "root";
        String password = "root";
        try{
            Connection connection = DriverManager.getConnection(jdbcUrl,username,password);
            String sqlString = "INSERT INTO TEST_SHARDING_ORDER (ORDER_ID, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, NOTE, ORDER_DATE, LAST_UPDATED_STAMP) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)";
            PreparedStatement preparedStatement = connection.prepareStatement(sqlString);
            preparedStatement.setString(1,idKeyValue);
            preparedStatement.setString(2,"customer");
            preparedStatement.setString(3,"supplier");
            preparedStatement.setString(4,"timestamp miss the million seconds");
            Timestamp currentTimestamp = new Timestamp(System.currentTimeMillis());
            System.out.println("currentTimestamp=="+currentTimestamp);
            preparedStatement.setTimestamp(5,currentTimestamp);//这里会因为MySQL jdbc driver this.connection.versionMeetsMinimum(5, 6, 4)数据库版本校验问题导致毫秒丢失
            preparedStatement.setTimestamp(6,currentTimestamp);//这里会因为MySQL jdbc driver this.connection.versionMeetsMinimum(5, 6, 4)数据库版本校验问题导致毫秒丢失
            preparedStatement.executeUpdate();

            preparedStatement.close();
            connection.close();
        }catch (Exception e){
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
```
when run this test,out put is
sharding is 3
currentTimestamp==2019-11-23 14:29:01.588

but the timestamp in database is 2019-11-23 14:29:01.0

the insert sql statement itself works fine, but the insert value of the timestamp will miss the milliseconds because of the db version checking in the mysql jdbc driver.

I do think ShardingProxy should let the jdbc driver know the real database's version.
e.g.
this.connection.versionMeetsMinimum(5, 6, 4) in the mysql jdbc driver should be true because my MySQL version is 5.7.25

or only run the sql in a client if you prefer

```
INSERT INTO TEST_SHARDING_ORDER
(ORDER_ID, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, NOTE, ORDER_DATE, LAST_UPDATED_STAMP)
VALUES('100008', 'customer', 'supplier', '会丢失毫秒', '2019-11-23 14:30:01.588', '2019-11-23 14:30:01.588');
```

